dct_title_s: Scarborough's map of Scotland, shewing counties, all railroad and steamship lines with distances between stations and landings
dct_description_sm: Includes lists of Scotland burghs and civil counties with 1901 census data.; Includes table of travel distances.; Inset: Shetland and Orkney Islands.; "No. 331" in upper left.; "Printed by the Scarborough Company, Boston, U.S.A." in lower left.
